### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Balance
GET {{baseUrl}}/balance/1A1zP1eP5QGefi2DMPTfTL5SLmv7DivfNa
Content-Type: application/json

