### Rollback to Height (basic)
POST {{baseUrl}}/rollback?height=2

### Rollback to Height (with timeout header)
POST {{baseUrl}}/rollback?height=2
x-block-ttl: 10000

### Rollback Error Example (invalid height - greater than current)
POST {{baseUrl}}/rollback?height=999

### Rollback Error Example (invalid height - negative)
POST {{baseUrl}}/rollback?height=-1

